com.gfycat.core.storage

Interface MediaFilesManager


  • public interface MediaFilesManager
    Provides access to Gfycat media cache files.

    !!! Warning: Cache files are for READ ONLY purpose. Do not modify or delete them!

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods

    • Method Detail

      • loadAsByteArray

        rx.Observable<byte[]> loadAsByteArray(Gfycat gfycat,
                                      MediaType mediaType)
        Allocates Gfycat media file as byte array into memory.

        Looks for a media file in cache. Downloads and saves it to one if not found.

        Parameters:
        gfycat - of media file to get.
        mediaType - type of media file to get.
        Returns:
        byte array of requested media file allocated in memory.

      • loadAsFile

        rx.Observable<File> loadAsFile(Gfycat gfycat,
                               MediaType mediaType)
        Get Gfycat media file.

        Looks for a media file in cache. Downloads and saves it to one if not found.

        !!! Warning: You MUST NOT modify or delete this file. Treat is as READ ONLY file.

        Parameters:
        gfycat - of media file to get.
        mediaType - type of media file to get.
        Returns:
        media file in cache.
